= Pebble Application for Madrid EMT Buses =

*Disclaimer*: This is not maintained and due to Pebble dissapearing, the app
not longer works.


This application queries the proxy EMT API, in that time the self-signed 
certificate by EMT was a really mess. By your cell phone location 
gives you the near bus stops.

You can select a bus stop number and you get the upcoming buses by line
number and destination.
